Class ShippingRate

java.lang.Object
com.stripe.model.StripeObject
com.stripe.net.ApiResource
com.stripe.model.ShippingRate
All Implemented Interfaces:
HasId, MetadataStore<ShippingRate>, StripeActiveObject, StripeObjectInterface
public class ShippingRate extends ApiResource implements HasId, MetadataStore<ShippingRate>
Shipping rates describe the price of shipping presented to your customers and applied to a purchase. For more information, see Charge for shipping.
